WEBVTT

00:09.120 --> 00:11.310
Wang Yingxue thinks
that she's intelligent.

00:12.330 --> 00:14.489
That's why I have to
be one step ahead of her.

00:14.490 --> 00:16.820
What the turtle shell shows
doesn't matter.

00:17.080 --> 00:18.210
Most importantly,

00:18.220 --> 00:20.230
we just need to cast doubts
in Wei Tingzhen's mind.

00:20.330 --> 00:21.610
Wei Tingzhen was always paranoid.

00:21.620 --> 00:23.879
Fourth Young Lady treats her nicely
out of the ordinary.

00:23.880 --> 00:25.359
She'll surely get to the bottom of it.

00:25.360 --> 00:27.329
So, what is she trying

00:27.330 --> 00:28.910
to get to the bottom of?

00:29.520 --> 00:31.079
That'll depend on the act

00:31.080 --> 00:32.590
you two have to stage for me.

00:33.890 --> 00:35.030
What?

00:35.440 --> 00:36.359
Infertility?

00:36.360 --> 00:37.569
Indeed.

00:37.570 --> 00:39.100
That day, I inquired
about Dou Zhao's

00:39.110 --> 00:41.569
condition from her maid as per your instructions.

00:41.570 --> 00:42.889
They told me everything

00:42.890 --> 00:44.569
after they got drunk.

00:44.570 --> 00:47.510
Miss Dou looked pale last time.

00:47.800 --> 00:50.209
Madam told me
to prepare some tonics

00:50.210 --> 00:51.740
for her.

00:53.160 --> 00:54.910
She has consumed countless tonics.

00:55.010 --> 00:56.700
But they never worked.

00:57.400 --> 00:58.540
No wonder

00:58.650 --> 01:00.719
you smell of medicine.

01:00.720 --> 01:01.929
I brew medicine

01:01.930 --> 01:03.460
in the kitchen every day.

01:03.760 --> 01:05.430
You do reek of medicine.

01:05.520 --> 01:06.870
So, what kind of condition

01:07.240 --> 01:08.649
is Miss Dou facing?

01:08.650 --> 01:09.820
It's just...

01:12.800 --> 01:14.070
Nanny, don't blame her.

01:14.360 --> 01:16.380
She's spouting nonsense
now that she's drunk.

01:16.690 --> 01:18.879
Fourth Young Lady is perfectly fine.

01:18.880 --> 01:20.460
She brewed the medicine for me.

01:20.690 --> 01:22.489
It's obvious that she was lying.

01:22.490 --> 01:23.660
No one will fall for that.

01:23.960 --> 01:25.489
I spent a lot of effort

01:25.490 --> 01:27.159
to tail them until the fifth watch.

01:27.160 --> 01:28.689
Then, I saw those two lasses

01:28.690 --> 01:30.599
bury a white sack

01:30.600 --> 01:31.900
under the tree.

01:35.800 --> 01:38.129
I brought it back
and inquired a herb expert.

01:38.130 --> 01:39.319
They said the doses are high.

01:39.320 --> 01:41.489
It must've been used

01:41.490 --> 01:43.820
on a woman who's infertile.

01:44.080 --> 01:45.079
Madam,

01:45.080 --> 01:46.790
you didn't see it for yourself,

01:46.850 --> 01:49.990
but the tree was scorched.

01:51.930 --> 01:53.799
It's no wonder one of them
were acting sneakily

01:53.800 --> 01:55.230
while the other changed her attitude.

01:55.320 --> 01:57.209
So, they knew that Dou Zhao
was infertile.

01:57.210 --> 01:59.950
They wish to marry her into our family
in case nobody wants her.

02:00.360 --> 02:01.790
That Wang Yingxue,

02:03.160 --> 02:05.260
how dare she disrespect
the forces of nature?

02:07.010 --> 02:09.230
Send the Dou Family a letter.

02:09.440 --> 02:11.780
Tell them to halt
the engagement for now.

02:12.370 --> 02:13.900
Since Dou Zhao is sick,

02:14.410 --> 02:16.870
the wedding date should be reconsidered.

02:17.440 --> 02:19.020
Let us see

02:19.370 --> 02:21.450
who it is that cannot afford the delay.

02:21.460 --> 02:22.729
(The wedding date can be reconsidered.)

02:22.730 --> 02:24.110
(Wei Tingzhen,
Duke of Jining's Residence)

02:27.680 --> 02:28.719
Madam, please be appeased.

02:28.720 --> 02:30.150
That Wei Tingzhen,

02:30.370 --> 02:31.830
what exactly is she up to?

02:41.160 --> 02:42.300
Extend your hand.

02:47.850 --> 02:49.550
What did Dou Zhao tell you?

02:49.850 --> 02:51.110
It's not her fault.

02:51.160 --> 02:53.670
I was the one who did something
that I wasn't supposed to.

02:53.850 --> 02:55.870
You useless fool!

02:56.600 --> 02:58.319
Duke of Jining has already advanced

02:58.320 --> 03:00.089
their stipend ten years into the future.

03:00.090 --> 03:02.689
Out of ten businesses,
nine of them incur losses.

03:02.690 --> 03:03.980
With Wei Tingyu's ability,

03:03.990 --> 03:06.310
do you think he's able to
repay his debt in this lifetime?

03:06.600 --> 03:08.319
I'm marrying Dou Zhao off

03:08.320 --> 03:10.940
to make her suffer from Wei Tingzhen.

03:10.950 --> 03:12.050
The Duke of Jing's Residence

03:12.060 --> 03:14.129
send out abused maidservants
every month, you know?

03:14.130 --> 03:15.740
Do you think it's a joke?

03:16.850 --> 03:18.809
I'm sure that Wei Tingyu tempted her.

03:18.810 --> 03:21.369
Ming has little knowledge of the world
as she was raised here.

03:21.370 --> 03:22.940
That's why she was duped.

03:25.040 --> 03:25.879
Fifth Young Lady,

03:25.880 --> 03:27.150
apologize now.

03:28.850 --> 03:30.310
Mother, I know my fault now.

03:33.760 --> 03:35.390
Do you truly know your fault?

03:37.120 --> 03:38.930
Or did you say so
because of the punishment?

03:39.290 --> 03:40.139
Mother,

03:40.140 --> 03:41.650
actually, His Lordship and I are...

03:42.480 --> 03:43.879
I'll tell you this.

03:43.880 --> 03:45.340
It's impossible between you two!

03:49.480 --> 03:50.620
Mother!

03:57.200 --> 03:59.369
Seventh Master was always
concerned about Young Lady.

03:59.370 --> 04:01.039
Fifth Master is the key here.

04:01.040 --> 04:02.620
It takes two to tango.

04:02.930 --> 04:05.020
Now, the Wei Family is the one
refusing the marriage.

04:05.290 --> 04:08.150
Fifth Uncle must
be acting drunk as usual.

04:08.250 --> 04:09.830
But Dou Ming is quite pitiful.

04:10.040 --> 04:12.550
Wang Yingxue has discovered
her relationship with Wei Tingyu.

04:13.370 --> 04:14.990
I assume she would be severely punished.

04:15.440 --> 04:17.470
Offer me some ice cream,

04:17.520 --> 04:20.990
and I'll avert the disasters
on your behalf.

04:26.170 --> 04:27.350
Ji Jianming,

04:27.690 --> 04:29.620
stop fooling around.

04:30.370 --> 04:31.700
What are you doing in the Capital?

04:34.630 --> 04:35.959
After the horse market was opened,

04:35.960 --> 04:37.630
all those foolish people
who want to fawn

04:37.640 --> 04:39.609
on us flocked to us in large groups.

04:39.610 --> 04:41.470
Naturally, I won't make friends
with them.

04:42.020 --> 04:44.129
Therefore, Lord Qing
sent me back to the Capital

04:44.130 --> 04:45.270
to report for duty.

04:46.440 --> 04:48.369
Polygonum multiflorum
and Rehmannia glutinosa?

04:48.370 --> 04:50.820
These are included in the prescription
for infertile women.

04:53.240 --> 04:54.630
Are you pretending to be infertile?

04:55.570 --> 04:57.820
When you stage an act,
you have to prepare the full show.

04:57.840 --> 04:59.489
Wei Tingzhen will only steel her resolve

04:59.490 --> 05:01.520
upon seeing the medicinal dregs.

05:01.530 --> 05:04.080
No wonder Seventh Uncle said
that the marriage was delayed again

05:04.090 --> 05:04.879
on our way back.

05:04.880 --> 05:06.570
But why did you go through all the trouble?

05:06.580 --> 05:09.049
You can tell me anytime
that you want to cancel the wedding.

05:09.050 --> 05:10.990
I have plenty of fast-acting methods.

05:12.080 --> 05:15.110
I'm good at getting rid
of bad luck in love.

05:15.250 --> 05:17.870
Family affairs are different
from state affairs.

05:18.440 --> 05:19.369
If we do it quick,

05:19.370 --> 05:20.959
other people might be implicated.

05:20.960 --> 05:22.209
And, the Wei Family is already

05:22.210 --> 05:24.270
looking for an excuse
to cancel the wedding.

05:24.400 --> 05:26.399
You better not do anything stupid.

05:26.400 --> 05:27.820
I don't need your help.

05:35.010 --> 05:36.150
I'll definitely help you.

06:59.670 --> 07:03.829
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

07:03.830 --> 07:06.989
=Episode 16=

07:06.990 --> 07:12.049
(Exquisite Melodies)

07:12.050 --> 07:13.670
- Excellent!
- Excellent!

07:13.810 --> 07:16.060
Excellent!

07:16.320 --> 07:18.870
As expected from the famous talent
in the Capital!

07:18.880 --> 07:20.020
Excellent!

07:21.820 --> 07:23.510
Your Highness,
what do you think about it?

07:24.250 --> 07:26.670
He's able to entertain
Your Highness and Your Lordship today.

07:26.820 --> 07:28.930
He's very blessed.

07:29.920 --> 07:31.519
Excellent.

07:31.520 --> 07:34.110
I never expected that the once
handsome young general

07:34.280 --> 07:36.910
is now obsessed with the play here.

07:37.370 --> 07:38.790
Your Highness, you may not know,

07:39.010 --> 07:41.009
ever since His Lordship
purchased Guanghe Tower,

07:41.010 --> 07:44.030
plays were held every day.

07:44.490 --> 07:47.430
Your Highness, what kinds
of plays do you like?

07:48.930 --> 07:51.990
Please don't stand on ceremony.

07:54.170 --> 07:55.500
Such audacity!

08:00.810 --> 08:01.950
Your Highness,

08:01.960 --> 08:03.319
The actors here

08:03.320 --> 08:04.519
are all spoiled by me.

08:04.520 --> 08:05.940
Please don't scare them.

08:06.480 --> 08:11.600
- Excellent!
- Excellent!

08:13.220 --> 08:16.110
You're still in the mourning period.
The entire court disapproves of you.

08:16.120 --> 08:18.180
What nonsense are you doing right now?

08:21.440 --> 08:23.729
His Majesty already spared me
from the mourning period.

08:23.730 --> 08:25.180
I have to obey his order.

08:25.250 --> 08:28.700
Besides, loyalty to the ruler
is the biggest part of filial piety.

08:31.370 --> 08:33.310
Excellent!

08:33.800 --> 08:35.790
I know you're laying low on purpose.

08:36.560 --> 08:38.559
You pretend to indulge
in worldly pleasures.

08:38.560 --> 08:41.340
In reality, you want people
to forget about your grudge

08:41.450 --> 08:42.590
and hatred.

08:45.680 --> 08:47.220
If you wish to investigate

08:47.970 --> 08:49.390
Duke of Ying's case,

08:49.930 --> 08:51.630
I might be able to help you out.

08:52.590 --> 08:56.130
(Exquisite Melodies)

08:57.470 --> 08:59.410
Uncle was killed by the pirates.

08:59.530 --> 09:01.090
His Majesty has already closed the case.

09:01.510 --> 09:05.250
Your Highness, could it be
that you have doubts about the case?

09:10.540 --> 09:14.509
- Excellent!
- Excellent!

09:14.510 --> 09:16.890
What about your father's plot
against you?

09:17.230 --> 09:18.690
Do you plan to let him off?

09:20.510 --> 09:23.490
We're family. Why would he set me up?

09:23.510 --> 09:24.389
To put it bluntly,

09:24.390 --> 09:26.069
he's my father.

09:26.070 --> 09:27.319
What can I do?

09:27.320 --> 09:28.949
At most, I can only manage

09:28.950 --> 09:32.050
the heirs and soldier ruffians
on the training ground.

09:32.390 --> 09:33.530
And,

09:33.810 --> 09:36.450
this paradise.

09:37.140 --> 09:39.219
- Excellent!
- Excellent!

09:39.220 --> 09:41.930
It's a waste of your talent.

09:42.990 --> 09:46.170
Your Highness, I guess I should
serve you with my abilities.

09:56.070 --> 09:57.770
It's inconvenient
to do this in the palace.

09:57.830 --> 09:59.170
Your Highness,

09:59.390 --> 10:01.349
I'll reserve some actors
for you in secret.

10:01.350 --> 10:03.290
What do you take me for?

10:04.250 --> 10:06.759
Earl of Yunyang and Princess Jingyu
value you highly, you know?

10:06.760 --> 10:08.210
They must've been blind!

10:09.390 --> 10:11.010
Your Highness, please come again.

10:14.070 --> 10:16.050
- Excellent!
- Excellent!

10:18.950 --> 10:21.120
Your Lordship, this is a brilliant idea.

10:21.130 --> 10:23.040
The officials in the Capital
love watching plays

10:23.050 --> 10:24.060
regardless of their ranks.

10:24.070 --> 10:25.700
We disguise ourselves
as a theater troupe

10:25.710 --> 10:28.050
to hide our tracks so that it's easier
to gather intel.

10:28.070 --> 10:30.690
Your Lordship, it's easier for us
to discuss things here too.

10:30.750 --> 10:33.210
However, all of you have to
let your martial arts go to waste

10:33.350 --> 10:34.690
and hide your identities.

10:34.750 --> 10:36.050
Sorry about this.

10:36.270 --> 10:37.930
Your Lordship, it's nothing.

10:39.110 --> 10:41.570
His Highness
visited us incognito to test us.

10:42.070 --> 10:43.890
He brought up the past on purpose

10:44.350 --> 10:47.050
not only to win you to his side.

10:48.910 --> 10:50.720
Your Lordship, during today's performance,

10:50.730 --> 10:52.829
the person in charge of hosting
the station officers

10:52.830 --> 10:54.470
have procured new leads unexpectedly.

10:54.480 --> 10:56.389
This person spoke with certainty
after drinking,

10:56.390 --> 10:58.110
claiming that the general had written
a letter

10:58.120 --> 10:59.970
to your mother
before he entered the Capital.

11:01.710 --> 11:04.490
No one noticed it since it wasn't sent
through the military post.

11:05.840 --> 11:07.483
I've checked the letters
in the residence

11:07.484 --> 11:08.850
after the fall of my family.

11:09.020 --> 11:10.330
Uncle didn't write us any letters.

11:10.870 --> 11:13.050
The letter vanished
upon arriving in the Capital.

11:13.120 --> 11:15.650
Even the person who delivered the letter
is nowhere to be seen.

11:16.150 --> 11:17.610
The Capital's station officer

11:17.630 --> 11:19.280
is the crown princess's cousin.

11:24.370 --> 11:25.610
Send someone to notify Chen Jia.

11:25.620 --> 11:28.700
Tell him to investigate the case and keep
a close eye on the Eastern Palace.

11:28.710 --> 11:30.549
Get acquainted
with His Highness's subjects,

11:30.550 --> 11:31.790
including his inner household.

11:33.310 --> 11:34.450
Yes, Your Lordship.

11:36.590 --> 11:41.450
(Lu's Dental Shop)

12:01.990 --> 12:04.079
(Su Yan, Rite Official)

12:04.080 --> 12:06.610
This is a 30-year-old Jinyin Wine.

12:36.420 --> 12:38.390
So,

12:38.870 --> 12:41.290
are you sure that the letter
Duke of Ding wrote to his family

12:42.210 --> 12:43.700
will pose no threat to us?

12:44.030 --> 12:47.650
Both Duke of Ding and the Ding Army
are already gone.

12:48.110 --> 12:50.389
It's just a letter to his family.

12:50.390 --> 12:52.610
What can it do?

12:55.710 --> 12:57.570
I wonder what
that rebellious son of mine

12:58.750 --> 13:00.810
will do now.

13:05.630 --> 13:06.890
Could it be that Mother's death

13:07.910 --> 13:09.090
is related to Uncle?

13:10.630 --> 13:12.410
Being convicted, assassinated,

13:12.510 --> 13:14.330
dying from illness, fall of the family,

13:14.670 --> 13:16.730
all of these events
occurred one after another.

13:18.330 --> 13:19.869
Not only must it be carefully examined,

13:19.870 --> 13:21.010
layer by layer,

13:21.030 --> 13:22.780
but it also requires
patience and endurance.

13:23.790 --> 13:26.130
Just like what
Fourth Young Lady Dou had said,

13:26.950 --> 13:29.010
we have to plan this through.

13:32.110 --> 13:33.109
Your Lordship!

13:33.110 --> 13:34.250
There's a situation outside.

13:39.070 --> 13:40.210
Where?

13:41.330 --> 13:43.629
Wei, you created this painting
through exquisite brushwork

13:43.630 --> 13:44.810
and clever use of ink.

13:44.910 --> 13:46.570
You're truly talented.

13:47.270 --> 13:48.359
Jianming,

13:48.360 --> 13:50.020
we should've known each other earlier.

13:50.290 --> 13:53.019
Your praise touches my heart deeply.

13:53.020 --> 13:54.770
Come. Let's have a toast.

13:55.670 --> 13:56.810
Come.

14:04.430 --> 14:05.570
Jianming,

14:05.590 --> 14:07.210
I'm deeply troubled.

14:07.610 --> 14:09.189
One can drown their sorrows with liquor.

14:09.190 --> 14:10.109
Tingyu,

14:10.110 --> 14:12.050
everything will be better
after you wake up.

14:12.350 --> 14:13.490
Come. Over here.

14:14.430 --> 14:15.339
Come.

14:15.340 --> 14:16.870
Jianming.

14:21.590 --> 14:24.130
Since when were they this close?

14:26.070 --> 14:27.069
Your Lordship,

14:27.070 --> 14:28.229
I saw Fifth Young Lady Dou

14:28.230 --> 14:29.510
entering Guanghe Tower just now.

14:29.670 --> 14:30.810
Dou Ming?

14:47.430 --> 14:48.589
That's the room.

14:48.590 --> 14:49.730
Thank you.

14:51.350 --> 14:53.370
- Excellent!
- Excellent!

14:53.430 --> 14:55.770
- Excellent!
- Excellent!

15:20.830 --> 15:21.990
Someone.

15:24.670 --> 15:26.090
Get me some water.

15:32.990 --> 15:34.130
Ming?

15:36.830 --> 15:38.370
Am I dreaming?

15:42.110 --> 15:44.050
Ming, you...

15:46.710 --> 15:47.970
What are you doing here?

15:48.670 --> 15:50.229
What exactly are you up to?

15:50.230 --> 15:51.640
Ji Jianming said with certainty

15:51.650 --> 15:53.580
that you wanted to see me
for an urgent matter.

15:53.590 --> 15:55.970
I rushed here after changing
into my maid's clothes.

15:56.430 --> 15:57.869
In the end, you were totally drunk.

15:57.870 --> 15:59.610
I wanted to get you
a bowl of hangover soup,

15:59.620 --> 16:01.430
but the door was locked!

16:05.270 --> 16:06.410
You're despicable!

16:06.470 --> 16:07.610
I...

16:10.150 --> 16:11.069
Something's off.

16:11.070 --> 16:13.010
Ji Yong was the one
who wanted to drink with me.

16:13.020 --> 16:14.650
Although I mentioned you
in front of him,

16:14.670 --> 16:16.330
I didn't tell him to invite you.

16:19.350 --> 16:20.490
This won't do.

16:20.710 --> 16:22.290
I have to clarify things with Ji Yong.

16:22.790 --> 16:23.930
Ji Yong!

16:24.990 --> 16:26.109
Open the door!

16:26.110 --> 16:27.570
I've tried everything.

16:27.670 --> 16:29.170
It's locked from the outside.

16:29.350 --> 16:30.650
There's no way to unlock it.

16:31.510 --> 16:32.650
This is...

16:34.190 --> 16:35.650
Ming, I...

16:38.390 --> 16:39.930
I have no such intentions.

16:40.790 --> 16:42.290
Although I'm playful,

16:42.870 --> 16:44.810
I would never resort
to such ploys and tricks.

16:44.870 --> 16:46.010
Moreover,

16:46.230 --> 16:47.570
you're my beloved.

16:48.280 --> 16:49.420
I...

16:50.720 --> 16:52.490
But there's no way
we can explain ourselves

16:52.860 --> 16:55.770
after spending the night here together.

16:56.110 --> 16:57.970
Who would open the door for us tomorrow?

16:58.110 --> 17:00.290
What will this rumor turn into
the day after tomorrow?

17:01.190 --> 17:03.170
The criticisms will drown me alive!

17:04.040 --> 17:07.419
Sister, Father, Mother, and Grandfather,

17:07.420 --> 17:09.020
all of them will be implicated.

17:11.050 --> 17:13.010
Why don't I just die right now?

17:13.230 --> 17:14.389
Ming!

17:14.390 --> 17:15.530
Don't do that!

17:21.470 --> 17:24.370
You risked everything to come here
because of me.

17:28.930 --> 17:30.210
If you cherish your reputation,

17:31.250 --> 17:32.810
I shall take my life together with you.

17:33.430 --> 17:35.029
Don't do it!

17:35.030 --> 17:35.880
Don't do this!

17:35.890 --> 17:36.989
You have a noble identity.

17:36.990 --> 17:38.300
You don't need to do this for me.

17:38.310 --> 17:38.949
Ming,

17:38.950 --> 17:40.089
I swore a vow before.

17:40.090 --> 17:41.570
You're the only woman I'll marry.

17:41.750 --> 17:44.090
Even if our parents are
separating us by force

17:44.100 --> 17:45.740
and that we aren't predestined
to be together,

17:45.750 --> 17:46.610
I wouldn't abandon you

17:48.290 --> 17:50.130
even if that means
we have to die together.

18:09.430 --> 18:12.650
Our parents gave birth to us.

18:12.950 --> 18:16.690
This is the command
of our parents that we have to follow.

18:33.550 --> 18:34.930
With our hair tied, we swear a vow.

18:35.120 --> 18:36.450
We shall not let each other down.

18:37.350 --> 18:40.490
Now, we don't even fear death.

18:41.630 --> 18:43.650
Why should we fear our feelings?

18:54.370 --> 18:55.810
It's a success.

19:00.430 --> 19:01.829
It's you again?

19:01.830 --> 19:02.909
Did I offend you?

19:02.910 --> 19:03.759
Have you considered

19:03.760 --> 19:05.970
Dou Zhao's feelings and circumstances
when you did so?

19:06.270 --> 19:08.350
Ordinary people can only
perceive what has happened,

19:08.360 --> 19:09.189
not what is to come.

19:09.190 --> 19:10.490
I'm helping Dou Zhao out.

19:11.750 --> 19:12.890
You...

19:18.390 --> 19:19.570
It's all my fault.

19:19.590 --> 19:20.589
Harm me if you wish.

19:20.590 --> 19:21.730
Do not touch her.

19:24.070 --> 19:25.399
(Duke of Jining's Residence)

19:25.400 --> 19:26.570
- Your Lordship.
- I'm fine.

19:26.580 --> 19:28.429
- Lu Ming, shut the door.
- Yes, sir.

19:28.430 --> 19:30.250
- Do not let anyone enter or exit.
- Yes, sir.

19:32.470 --> 19:33.309
Tingyu!

19:33.310 --> 19:35.029
Why did they beat you up?

19:35.030 --> 19:38.109
Song Mo, Tingyu has already relieved himself
of the Imperial Guard's duty.

19:38.110 --> 19:39.759
What gives you the right to hit him?

19:39.760 --> 19:41.189
Tingzhen, it's all my fault.

19:41.190 --> 19:43.109
You better mind your words
and your servants'.

19:43.110 --> 19:44.820
His Lordship got lost
in the middle of the night.

19:44.830 --> 19:46.250
He fell by accident.

19:46.790 --> 19:48.530
I sent him back out of kind intentions.

19:48.750 --> 19:51.850
That's the only statement
you should reveal to the public.

19:58.950 --> 20:02.050
If a single word of this gets out,

20:02.590 --> 20:04.570
I'll come back and cut off your tongue.

20:07.350 --> 20:08.490
Understood.

20:14.430 --> 20:15.890
What exactly is going on?

20:16.830 --> 20:18.389
You...

20:18.390 --> 20:19.469
- Tingzhen.
- You...

20:19.470 --> 20:20.890
I cannot marry Dou Zhao.

20:20.930 --> 20:22.709
Tingzhen, please allow me
to marry Dou Ming.

20:22.710 --> 20:23.850
You!

20:28.030 --> 20:29.570
Wang Yingxue.

20:30.710 --> 20:32.570
You vicious wretch!

20:32.580 --> 20:34.890
Since your eldest daughter
couldn't marry into the family,

20:35.020 --> 20:37.290
you set up my son to make him
marry your second daughter!

20:37.470 --> 20:40.090
Now, you've become
a parasite of the Wei Family!

20:41.710 --> 20:43.509
(Duke of Jining's Residence)
Your Lordship,

20:43.510 --> 20:45.789
he's indeed a playboy

20:45.790 --> 20:47.410
who's greedy and lustful.

20:47.430 --> 20:49.509
Why don't we take advantage
of the situation?

20:49.510 --> 20:51.650
Wei Tingyu is a scoundrel indeed.

20:51.660 --> 20:54.170
However, his engagement
with Dou Zhao hasn't been canceled yet.

20:54.390 --> 20:56.090
If news of this gets out,

20:56.190 --> 20:57.810
she'll be mocked and ridiculed

20:57.870 --> 20:59.410
for the rest of her life.

21:00.250 --> 21:02.450
What happened to the Wu family
was the perfect example.

21:02.590 --> 21:03.930
But if we send Wei Tingyu back,

21:03.940 --> 21:06.509
doesn't that mean Fourth Young Lady Dou
has to be married to him?

21:06.510 --> 21:07.650
He can try it if he dares.

21:09.310 --> 21:11.970
I need to escort His Majesty
to the western mountains in a few days.

21:12.710 --> 21:14.090
I need to come up with a solution.

21:15.750 --> 21:18.330
(Universal Compassion)

21:18.390 --> 21:19.530
Mother,

21:19.750 --> 21:20.789
I don't wish to go.

21:20.790 --> 21:22.690
- I'm not going to the temple!
- Just go!

21:23.510 --> 21:25.189
(Wanfo Temple)
Go!

21:25.190 --> 21:26.690
I'm not going!

21:26.710 --> 21:28.490
- Just go!
- Enough. Stop messing around.

21:29.150 --> 21:31.110
You can live in the temple
for a few days first.

21:31.550 --> 21:34.170
If other people ask about you,
say that you're on a retreat.

21:34.470 --> 21:35.980
As for the incident in Guanghe Tower,

21:35.990 --> 21:37.410
treat it as if it never took place.

21:37.670 --> 21:38.810
Mother,

21:38.910 --> 21:41.159
although His Lordship
and I did nothing, I...

21:41.160 --> 21:43.570
Shut up! Even if
you're not embarrassed, I am!

21:45.580 --> 21:47.810
I've already sent our men
to Duke of Jining's Residence.

21:48.120 --> 21:50.390
I'm urging the Wei Family
to decide on the wedding date.

21:50.600 --> 21:52.170
For the sake of the three families,

21:53.100 --> 21:54.470
Dou Zhao

21:55.150 --> 21:56.370
must be married to him.

21:57.470 --> 21:58.610
Mother,

21:59.000 --> 22:00.140
I've always been

22:00.310 --> 22:02.130
leading a cautious life since young.

22:02.570 --> 22:04.290
I endured everything I could.

22:04.630 --> 22:05.870
Not this time.

22:06.170 --> 22:08.450
His Lordship and I have already
sworn a vow with our hair.

22:08.460 --> 22:10.309
Mother, I wish to act
without hesitations,

22:10.310 --> 22:12.650
just like how you got married
to Father bravely.

22:15.430 --> 22:17.490
Child, how could you be so silly?

22:17.950 --> 22:19.090
Men

22:19.430 --> 22:20.979
only cherish the things

22:20.980 --> 22:22.370
that are difficult to get.

22:23.790 --> 22:27.970
Back then, I got married to him
out of impulse and passion.

22:28.430 --> 22:30.189
Now, only desolateness awaits me.

22:30.190 --> 22:33.229
All these years of estranged marriage
and the incidents in the residence,

22:33.230 --> 22:34.989
weren't they clear enough
for you to see?

22:34.990 --> 22:37.130
Why are you trying
to follow in my footsteps?

22:37.550 --> 22:38.690
Mother,

22:38.790 --> 22:40.170
since young,

22:40.310 --> 22:43.010
you forced me to learn
how to write, draw, and obey the rules.

22:43.350 --> 22:45.610
Was it because it'd help me
obtain happiness?

22:45.620 --> 22:48.000
Or was it because it'd help me
to marry into a noble family

22:48.010 --> 22:49.890
so that I could
bring glory to the family?

22:51.310 --> 22:52.450
What did you say?

22:52.750 --> 22:54.890
You made me embroider
all those landscape paintings

22:54.910 --> 22:56.910
and gifted them to people
all across the Capital!

22:56.920 --> 22:59.330
But you only criticize me
for the mistakes I made.

22:59.390 --> 23:01.450
To you, I am never good enough!

23:02.070 --> 23:04.650
Only this time, only Wei Tingyu,

23:05.110 --> 23:07.090
he could see the wounds on my hand.

23:07.430 --> 23:09.269
He would tell me that I did great!

23:09.270 --> 23:11.290
I don't need to suffer anymore!

23:12.430 --> 23:16.090
I've raised you for over a decade!

23:16.150 --> 23:19.170
Now, you're infatuated with Wei Tingyu
all because of his fancy words?

23:20.790 --> 23:22.570
I'll tell you one last thing.

23:24.070 --> 23:27.650
One's fondness won't last forever.

23:28.070 --> 23:29.370
It'll fade away eventually.

23:29.630 --> 23:32.770
The only thing that can
ensure your future

23:33.190 --> 23:34.810
is a man's future

23:34.870 --> 23:36.090
and money!

23:36.430 --> 23:37.709
(Wanfo Temple)
Mother!

23:37.710 --> 23:39.210
Mother, I beg you!

23:39.390 --> 23:41.410
Mother, I don't want to go!

23:41.630 --> 23:42.970
Mother!

23:43.190 --> 23:44.890
You'll wake up from your dream

23:45.350 --> 23:46.970
once your sister gets married.

23:47.070 --> 23:48.250
Take her inside!

23:48.550 --> 23:49.469
- Let's go.
- Mother!

23:49.470 --> 23:50.349
- Ming.
- Mother!

23:50.350 --> 23:51.520
- Ming, let's go!
- Let's go!

23:51.530 --> 23:52.909
Mother, don't send me there!

23:52.910 --> 23:53.909
Ming, let's go.

23:53.910 --> 23:55.789
- Mother!
- Let's go!

23:55.790 --> 23:58.229
Mother, don't send me there!

23:58.230 --> 23:59.450
Mother!

24:00.350 --> 24:02.530
Mother, I don't want to go!

24:03.230 --> 24:04.949
(Wanfo Temple)
Mother!

24:04.950 --> 24:06.330
Mother!

24:18.950 --> 24:20.090
Madam.

24:21.070 --> 24:23.010
You're here. Have a seat.

24:29.510 --> 24:30.970
Duchess of Ying,

24:30.990 --> 24:32.189
I came here again

24:32.190 --> 24:35.210
to re-discuss the marriage
of our children.

24:36.390 --> 24:37.690
The tea

24:39.310 --> 24:40.530
may smell nice,

24:43.710 --> 24:46.130
but it's tasteless.

24:46.550 --> 24:49.730
Could it be that someone
has pulled a switcheroo?

24:50.230 --> 24:51.810
Madam, please practice wise judgment.

24:51.950 --> 24:54.050
I'm sure it wasn't us.

24:54.110 --> 24:55.650
I assume it was an outsider.

24:56.870 --> 24:57.989
Madam,

24:57.990 --> 24:59.069
I came here

24:59.070 --> 25:01.589
to clarify
the misunderstanding with you.

25:01.590 --> 25:02.730
Misunderstanding?

25:02.790 --> 25:03.649
Don't think

25:03.650 --> 25:05.010
that I don't know what you did.

25:05.150 --> 25:07.840
The Dou Family seems to have latched
onto our family, huh?

25:07.850 --> 25:08.949
Your eldest daughter failed.

25:08.950 --> 25:11.070
And now, you're asking
your second daughter to do so.

25:11.080 --> 25:11.879
Listen.

25:11.880 --> 25:14.050
The Wei Family isn't that gullible.

25:16.150 --> 25:17.290
Madam,

25:17.590 --> 25:18.930
please be appeased.

25:20.110 --> 25:21.610
I came here to tell you this.

25:21.790 --> 25:23.970
Dou Zhao is not only virtuous.

25:24.070 --> 25:25.850
She's also very wealthy.

25:26.070 --> 25:29.029
By then, you'll enjoy a luxurious life.

25:29.030 --> 25:30.330
Think about it.

25:30.470 --> 25:32.029
Once she marries into your family,

25:32.030 --> 25:33.290
you can take over

25:33.590 --> 25:36.490
all of her assets and wealth.

25:40.750 --> 25:42.610
As for Zhao's body,

25:43.830 --> 25:46.450
with enough time and careful nurturing,

25:47.030 --> 25:48.730
it'll definitely recover.

25:48.910 --> 25:50.050
You should try it again.

25:54.870 --> 25:56.730
I've already picked a date.

25:56.790 --> 26:00.130
Ten days from on is an auspicious day.

26:08.230 --> 26:10.930
Ruin one's reputation
so that you can reap the benefit, huh?

26:11.120 --> 26:13.170
You think you're the smartest man
in the world, huh?

26:13.390 --> 26:14.989
To think that you were educated.

26:14.990 --> 26:16.490
How dare you act so arrogantly?

26:16.590 --> 26:18.330
You act without thinking of the others.

26:18.340 --> 26:20.020
Luckily, it didn't blow
out of proportion.

26:20.030 --> 26:22.770
Do you think Dou Ming can stay alive
if everyone knows it?

26:23.430 --> 26:25.170
If you keep worrying about everything,

26:25.180 --> 26:27.110
then you deserve
to bear the grievances yourself.

26:27.270 --> 26:28.789
Do you think I need to stoop that low

26:28.790 --> 26:30.669
if you're willing to marry Wei Tingyu?

26:30.670 --> 26:32.410
It's true that I'm not willing
to marry him.

26:32.420 --> 26:33.810
But I have a thorough plan.

26:33.990 --> 26:35.909
I was one step away
from achieving success.

26:35.910 --> 26:37.170
But you insisted on interfering!

26:37.180 --> 26:40.020
All your methods are either feigning
sickness or pretending to be dead.

26:40.030 --> 26:41.370
You call that a thorough plan?

26:41.870 --> 26:43.509
At least I didn't harm people

26:43.510 --> 26:44.770
because of my selfish desires.

26:45.070 --> 26:48.730
How is what you're doing any different
from Wang Yingxue back then?

26:49.120 --> 26:50.870
How dare you compare me
with Wang Yingxue?

26:51.030 --> 26:52.400
My method yields immediate results.

26:52.410 --> 26:53.730
If you're willing to cancel,

26:53.750 --> 26:56.740
it doesn't matter even if Dou Ming and
Wei Tingyu have to suffer criticisms.

26:56.750 --> 26:58.669
It's Song Mo didn't meddle in,

26:58.670 --> 26:59.829
they'll thank me

26:59.830 --> 27:01.210
with wedding sweets.

27:01.630 --> 27:03.090
I did it for your sake, you know?

27:03.350 --> 27:04.610
Luckily, Song Mo was there.

27:05.230 --> 27:07.310
If not, the entire Dou Family
would've been done for.

27:07.390 --> 27:09.810
You said you did it for my sake.

27:09.830 --> 27:12.129
But have you ever considered
what I desired?

27:12.130 --> 27:13.810
It's pointless
no matter what you desire.

27:14.220 --> 27:16.370
If you do get married to Wei Tingyu,

27:16.510 --> 27:17.869
they'll still do the same thing

27:17.870 --> 27:19.170
under your nose, you know?

27:23.030 --> 27:24.170
Don't worry.

27:24.190 --> 27:25.330
The physician said

27:25.350 --> 27:27.050
she doesn't have much time left.

27:27.130 --> 27:29.090
Once she's dead,
and the mourning period is over,

27:29.110 --> 27:30.250
I'll marry you.

27:32.590 --> 27:34.109
I'm just helping the fruits on the tree

27:34.110 --> 27:35.450
to ripen faster.

27:35.760 --> 27:37.990
If you don't get away from Wei Tingyu,

27:38.130 --> 27:39.650
you'll definitely suffer in the future.

27:40.670 --> 27:42.410
I just don't want you

27:42.630 --> 27:43.890
to shed tears in the future.

27:45.910 --> 27:47.050
That's right.

27:47.670 --> 27:48.930
Everything you said was right.

27:49.830 --> 27:51.090
But I don't want to hear them.

27:52.190 --> 27:53.229
I'm too petty!

27:53.230 --> 27:54.810
I can't tolerate your demeanor!

27:54.820 --> 27:55.949
I don't wish to get involved

27:55.950 --> 27:59.110
with a despicable person like you who
tries to ruin other people's reputations!

28:00.950 --> 28:02.290
From now on,

28:03.270 --> 28:04.749
you and I

28:04.750 --> 28:06.050
will go our separate ways.

28:07.510 --> 28:08.770
Fine, Dou Zhao.

28:08.890 --> 28:11.610
You better don't come to me
when you get into trouble in the future!

28:28.410 --> 28:30.490
We just brought
Fifth Young Lady back not long ago.

28:30.550 --> 28:32.330
The moment
I took my eyes off her, she...

28:34.830 --> 28:35.970
Ming!

28:36.710 --> 28:37.850
Ming!

28:42.390 --> 28:43.970
Keep your mouth shut.

28:47.070 --> 28:48.210
Thank goodness!

28:48.630 --> 28:50.690
Hurry, get her some tea.

28:50.750 --> 28:51.890
Yes, Madam.

28:52.470 --> 28:53.850
Ming, are you okay?

28:54.030 --> 28:55.170
Mother,

28:55.750 --> 28:57.130
I'm an unfilial girl.

28:57.950 --> 28:59.429
Just let me die.

28:59.430 --> 29:00.570
No!

29:01.510 --> 29:02.650
No!

29:03.030 --> 29:04.340
Silly girl,

29:04.710 --> 29:06.010
in this world,

29:06.240 --> 29:09.250
there's no man
worth sacrificing your life for,

29:09.430 --> 29:11.490
not to mention a man like Wei Tingyu!

29:11.630 --> 29:13.450
Maybe he's not good enough.

29:14.350 --> 29:15.389
But...

29:15.390 --> 29:16.970
But one man's meat

29:17.750 --> 29:19.290
is another man's poison.

29:20.990 --> 29:22.970
We had already sworn an oath

29:23.310 --> 29:24.890
when we made our lifetime commitment.

29:25.550 --> 29:27.810
If we cannot grow old together,

29:28.450 --> 29:30.310
we shall accompany each other
in the afterlife.

29:30.430 --> 29:31.570
No!

29:32.470 --> 29:33.610
No!

29:44.790 --> 29:46.669
(Western Mountain Palace)

29:46.670 --> 29:49.370
Song Mo, there are about six routes
that can take us to this place.

29:49.380 --> 29:51.020
(Wealth and Luxury)
You took a detour on purpose

29:51.030 --> 29:51.869
so that I could see

29:51.870 --> 29:54.850
the lands under
Duke of Jining's rule are barren,

29:54.860 --> 29:57.210
and the common people
are chewing on tree bark to survive.

29:57.730 --> 29:59.990
You were targeting
Duke of Jining's Residence all along.

30:00.590 --> 30:02.210
Such audacity.

30:02.230 --> 30:04.170
How dare you abuse your power?

30:05.670 --> 30:08.330
Indeed. I was selfish
for changing the route.

30:08.710 --> 30:10.069
But Your Majesty, as you can see,

30:10.070 --> 30:12.730
Duchess of Jing forcibly requisitioned
the harvest from that area

30:12.750 --> 30:14.570
to arrange Duke of Jining's marriage.

30:14.670 --> 30:15.789
Now, the farmers

30:15.790 --> 30:17.690
don't even have rice seeds
to sow during spring.

30:17.790 --> 30:19.010
That's a fact.

30:19.250 --> 30:20.690
It's not something I've fabricated.

30:21.270 --> 30:24.490
The imperial family extorts the people
whenever there's a joyous occasion.

30:24.750 --> 30:26.070
This trend, if encouraged,

30:26.110 --> 30:28.210
will surely be copied by nobles
in other regions.

30:28.430 --> 30:30.570
The people's resentment
will be harder to resolve.

30:30.930 --> 30:32.700
Your Majesty,
please practice wise judgment.

30:32.710 --> 30:34.709
Wei Tingyu, relying on
his hereditary annual stipend,

30:34.710 --> 30:36.530
has achieved no notable accomplishments
over the years.

30:36.550 --> 30:38.410
He did all kinds
of ridiculous things instead.

30:38.590 --> 30:41.070
He's not worthy of the winner
of the Ladies' Etiquette Contest.

30:42.270 --> 30:43.730
You know clearly

30:44.550 --> 30:47.810
that I intend to grant you
and Jingyu a marriage.

30:48.630 --> 30:50.330
Don't tell me you intend
to marry Dou Zhao?

30:51.230 --> 30:54.069
The betrothal letters of the two
have been exchanged.

30:54.070 --> 30:55.909
I won't allow you to do what you want.

30:55.910 --> 30:57.050
If you intend to kneel,

30:58.670 --> 30:59.850
you can kneel here.

31:00.190 --> 31:02.050
Dou Zhao had no choice but to do so.

31:02.060 --> 31:04.180
She tried to cancel the marriage
several times but to no avail.

31:04.190 --> 31:05.989
I've almost lost all the people

31:05.990 --> 31:07.870
I have wanted to protect
and save in my life.

31:08.070 --> 31:10.090
This is the only wish I have.

31:10.590 --> 31:13.170
It's harmless to the imperial family
and to others.

31:13.910 --> 31:15.810
I only wish that the person I care about

31:16.270 --> 31:18.010
can have her wish fulfilled
just this once.

31:37.990 --> 31:39.740
By then, when the palanquin
crosses the bridge,

31:39.750 --> 31:41.570
I'll use this to burn it down.

31:42.270 --> 31:44.930
By then, you guys can push
the palanquin into the lake.

31:45.030 --> 31:46.450
I shall escape by swimming.

31:48.030 --> 31:50.650
It's covered with fragments of flint.

31:50.750 --> 31:53.090
And you need to jump into the lake
and escape by swimming.

31:53.270 --> 31:56.730
This is indeed a risky plan.

31:57.110 --> 31:58.149
Fourth Young Lady,

31:58.150 --> 32:00.970
why can't you just seek
Old Madam Cui's help?

32:01.910 --> 32:03.370
Grandmother is old now.

32:03.790 --> 32:05.810
And, she's often sick as well.

32:07.110 --> 32:09.450
I don't want her
to worry about me anymore.

32:13.910 --> 32:15.050
Miss.

32:15.190 --> 32:17.120
Wang Yingxue instructed several nannies

32:17.130 --> 32:19.110
to purchase the wedding gown
and accessories a few days ago.

32:20.350 --> 32:22.290
Anyway, the marriage won't take place.

32:22.420 --> 32:24.149
She can act as
the female head of the family

32:24.150 --> 32:25.029
all she likes.

32:25.030 --> 32:26.189
I heard

32:26.190 --> 32:28.309
that Wang Yingxue hired the best tailor

32:28.310 --> 32:29.770
to make another wedding gown.

32:29.830 --> 32:31.290
It wasn't your size.

32:39.630 --> 32:41.250
Ever since the founding of our nation,

32:41.950 --> 32:43.130
women

32:43.670 --> 32:45.250
could only wear this crown

32:45.630 --> 32:47.290
during their wedding.

32:48.670 --> 32:50.450
I've never worn it before.

32:53.990 --> 32:56.090
I hope that you can wear it tomorrow

32:56.710 --> 32:58.890
so that you can lead
a smooth and peaceful life.

33:05.750 --> 33:06.890
Mother,

33:08.110 --> 33:10.090
are you sure you want me
to replace Zhao?

33:14.430 --> 33:15.570
Ming,

33:18.710 --> 33:20.010
you're my flesh and blood.

33:21.350 --> 33:22.650
You're a part of me.

33:23.230 --> 33:25.490
How can I bear to see you die?

33:25.830 --> 33:26.970
Mother.

33:47.150 --> 33:48.530
Dou Ming's voice sounded strange.

33:49.020 --> 33:51.110
I assume she inflicted injury
upon herself as resistance.

33:51.710 --> 33:53.290
Wang Yingxue is helpless

33:53.990 --> 33:56.290
because she's her biological child.

33:57.510 --> 33:58.549
That's great.

33:58.550 --> 34:00.650
Miss, you don't need
to take the risk too.

34:01.150 --> 34:02.789
But Miss,

34:02.790 --> 34:05.090
you don't seem happy about it.

34:06.110 --> 34:08.330
I'm doing everything I can
to cancel the wedding.

34:08.920 --> 34:11.450
But she's doing everything she can
to get married to her beloved.

34:11.950 --> 34:13.570
Both of us are fighting
for our own futures.

34:15.510 --> 34:17.250
It's just that Duke of Jining's family

34:17.430 --> 34:19.050
is utterly rotten.

34:19.950 --> 34:22.130
Wei Tingyu isn't someone
whom she can entrust herself to.

34:24.190 --> 34:26.850
(Dou Ming hasn't harmed me
in this life.)

34:27.630 --> 34:29.810
(I can't just stand idly by
as she falls to her demise.)

34:38.190 --> 34:40.629
(Dou's Residence)

34:40.630 --> 34:42.090
Congratulations.

34:43.550 --> 34:44.690
His Lordship has arrived.

34:44.750 --> 34:46.019
(Bless)
It's so grand.

34:46.020 --> 34:47.160
- They're here.
- Congratulations, Your Lordship.

34:47.510 --> 34:48.669
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations, Your Lordship.

34:48.670 --> 34:50.330
Congratulations, Your Lordship.

35:08.390 --> 35:09.530
Zhao.

35:12.741 --> 35:14.770
The ceremony
will take up the entire day.

35:15.670 --> 35:16.970
I was afraid that you might starve.

35:17.070 --> 35:18.850
I've brought you some food.

35:24.430 --> 35:25.570
Su Lan,

35:25.710 --> 35:26.930
you may leave first.

35:27.110 --> 35:28.250
Yes.

35:37.870 --> 35:39.570
This is the lotus seed
and lily bulb dessert.

35:40.270 --> 35:43.890
It symbolizes a harmonious union
and a happy future.

35:46.150 --> 35:47.509
I wish you happiness

35:47.510 --> 35:48.810
and a smooth life ahead as well.

35:49.230 --> 35:50.810
May you find the one you love.

36:00.030 --> 36:01.279
Congratulations.

36:01.280 --> 36:02.920
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations.

36:05.120 --> 36:06.570
Ming hasn't recovered from her illness.

36:06.750 --> 36:08.570
She's unable to attend
her sister's wedding.

36:08.950 --> 36:10.090
What a shame.

36:10.270 --> 36:11.570
Don't worry.

36:12.120 --> 36:13.709
Later, I'll definitely
find a good husband

36:13.710 --> 36:15.770
for Ming as well.

36:24.620 --> 36:26.990
To think that I thought
she had something brilliant planned.

36:27.150 --> 36:28.930
In the end, she still
got into the palanquin.

36:32.550 --> 36:33.690
Wait!

36:38.710 --> 36:39.850
From now on,

36:41.270 --> 36:42.730
you must do well in life, okay?

36:43.430 --> 36:44.570
Go now.

36:53.270 --> 36:54.770
It's a facade, huh?

36:59.470 --> 37:01.850
Mr. Ji, you're intelligent indeed.

37:03.510 --> 37:05.029
I just wonder if that one

37:05.030 --> 37:06.450
is intelligent enough to realize this.

37:06.990 --> 37:10.890
(Duke of Jining's Residence)

37:14.510 --> 37:17.650
(Duke of Jining's Residence)

37:18.150 --> 37:19.290
Wait!

37:39.390 --> 37:40.530
Your Lordship,

37:40.630 --> 37:42.050
today's my wedding day.

37:42.670 --> 37:43.810
What are you doing?

37:45.820 --> 37:47.389
Dumb mantis, don't try anything stupid.

37:47.390 --> 37:48.730
- Do you know that...
- I know.

37:48.750 --> 37:49.890
That's not Dou Zhao.

37:50.630 --> 37:52.170
Why are you stopping them, then?

37:52.710 --> 37:53.970
I just found out not long ago.

37:54.870 --> 37:56.010
I knew

37:56.110 --> 37:57.930
she would never get married
to Wei Tingyu.

38:01.390 --> 38:03.189
(Misty Beauty)
This is their wedding. What is he...

38:03.190 --> 38:05.260
I heard that their families
had grudges against each other.

38:05.270 --> 38:06.410
Is that so?

38:06.430 --> 38:07.669
Why did they head inside?

38:07.670 --> 38:09.090
I don't know what's going on.

38:30.870 --> 38:33.050
All those couples who had
made a vow with their hair,

38:34.110 --> 38:36.170
how many of them
truly had feelings for each other?

38:37.070 --> 38:39.130
They just got married because
they had no choice.

38:43.470 --> 38:45.770
Sad, sleepless, in the long night,

38:46.870 --> 38:50.730
in separation, I think of you.

38:52.190 --> 38:54.850
Alas, I cannot hold the moonlight
in my slender hand.

38:55.630 --> 38:59.210
I go back into the room,
perhaps to dream again of reunion.

39:16.270 --> 39:17.410
Ming?

39:17.950 --> 39:19.170
It's you?

39:29.750 --> 39:30.749
This is great.

39:30.750 --> 39:32.290
How did the heavens send you to me?

39:39.820 --> 39:41.570
This dessert is important
for this occasion.

39:42.040 --> 39:43.490
There should be more of it.

39:43.590 --> 39:44.730
Get me another bowl.

39:45.950 --> 39:46.979
Zhao,

39:46.980 --> 39:48.239
I'm too ashamed to face you.

39:48.240 --> 39:49.960
I don't want it to be like this either.

39:52.950 --> 39:54.090
Dou Ming,

39:54.470 --> 39:56.890
one's marriage determines
a lifetime of happiness or sorrow.

39:56.990 --> 39:58.250
You have to think twice.

39:58.590 --> 40:00.770
Duke of Jining's Residence
is complicated and messy.

40:01.710 --> 40:03.690
And, Wei Tingyu isn't a good man.

40:03.910 --> 40:05.109
If you do get married to him,

40:05.110 --> 40:07.610
you might have to manage
the residence for the rest of your life.

40:07.620 --> 40:08.749
You might soon see through

40:08.750 --> 40:10.570
Wei Tingyu's cowardice and weakness.

40:11.110 --> 40:13.050
You might suffer a lot.

40:13.070 --> 40:14.910
You two might even
fall out of love after this.

40:15.110 --> 40:16.450
Have you thought of that?

40:17.270 --> 40:18.810
If you change your mind now,

40:19.030 --> 40:20.410
I can still do something about it.

40:22.510 --> 40:23.850
Since young,

40:24.710 --> 40:26.330
I always listened to Mother.

40:27.550 --> 40:31.170
I wanted to be a daughter
who she can be proud of.

40:31.870 --> 40:33.610
But no one was ever concerned about

40:33.910 --> 40:35.370
what I was thinking

40:35.830 --> 40:37.290
or what I liked.

40:38.870 --> 40:41.770
Mr. Wei is the first person

40:42.350 --> 40:46.130
to admire me wholeheartedly
and know me well.

40:48.510 --> 40:49.890
I like him.

40:51.710 --> 40:53.900
He's not a despicable person.

40:54.550 --> 40:56.570
It's just that his elder sister
is suppressing him.

40:56.790 --> 40:59.090
He went against his sister for my sake.

40:59.950 --> 41:01.410
He's devoted to me

41:01.550 --> 41:02.690
and trying his best.

41:02.870 --> 41:04.970
I think people can change.

41:05.430 --> 41:06.570
I'm changing.

41:06.750 --> 41:08.010
His Lordship is changing too.

41:08.720 --> 41:11.470
He has already dismissed the concubines
in the household for my sake.

41:12.390 --> 41:13.570
Isn't it possible

41:14.070 --> 41:15.909
that people will change for the better

41:15.910 --> 41:17.570
after what they've experienced?

41:19.670 --> 41:20.810
(Change, huh?)

41:22.710 --> 41:23.850
This time,

41:24.790 --> 41:26.890
I don't want to follow
other people's will.

41:27.030 --> 41:28.810
I only wish to act according

41:30.310 --> 41:31.450
to my heart.

41:32.750 --> 41:34.370
If you've made up your mind
to get married,

41:35.390 --> 41:36.530
I shall give you my blessings.

41:37.990 --> 41:39.389
- This won't do.
- Hurry up.

41:39.390 --> 41:41.010
We won't make it in time
when they're here.

41:41.030 --> 41:42.629
- Hurry, take this.
- I'm scared.

41:42.630 --> 41:43.890
- Hurry.
- No...

41:46.870 --> 41:48.010
Zhao!

41:48.670 --> 41:50.349
Are you okay? Was that too harsh?

41:50.350 --> 41:52.730
You actually hit me for real?

41:54.270 --> 41:55.930
Zhao, I'm sorry.

41:58.270 --> 41:59.410
Be careful.

42:08.150 --> 42:10.490
I've let Zhao down my entire life.

42:11.270 --> 42:13.570
If a person only has
a limited number of blessings,

42:14.230 --> 42:16.739
I'm willing to give Zhao
my remaining blessings.

42:16.740 --> 42:19.030
♪I rise on tiptoes♪

42:19.430 --> 42:20.789
I knocked her out

42:20.790 --> 42:22.349
and got into the palanquin
on her behalf.

42:22.350 --> 42:23.909
Tomorrow, people will surely mock me

42:23.910 --> 42:26.250
for belittling myself
and violating moral principles.

42:27.910 --> 42:29.050
Dear,

42:29.590 --> 42:31.450
you're willing to commit
such a drastic act for me.

42:32.390 --> 42:33.610
I will never forget

42:34.470 --> 42:35.890
your kindness.

42:36.910 --> 42:39.850
(From now on,
no matter how tough our lives will be,)

42:40.150 --> 42:41.669
(I'll always watch over you.)

42:41.670 --> 42:43.450
(I won't let you suffer again.)

42:45.400 --> 42:51.170
♪Not heeding the people's advice♪

42:51.680 --> 42:58.070
♪Our love is as clear as the moon,
no false words in sight♪

42:58.580 --> 43:03.929
♪I close our distance without rest♪

43:03.930 --> 43:09.050
♪I devote my life
and world to your wishes♪

43:09.340 --> 43:12.229
♪Not afraid of our encounter♪

43:12.230 --> 43:14.549
Why don't we make the Wei Family
acknowledge the marriage?

43:14.550 --> 43:15.549
Ms. Longevity was supposed

43:15.550 --> 43:16.720
to marry into their family.

43:16.730 --> 43:19.149
Isn't it reasonable for us to deliver more dowries
to them on Ming's behalf?

43:19.150 --> 43:20.530
Now that this had happened,

43:20.710 --> 43:22.589
you're questioning me instead?

43:22.590 --> 43:24.110
Do you even have
any regard for the Dou Family?

43:24.150 --> 43:25.029
Shut up!

43:25.030 --> 43:26.829
Who will give Ms. Longevity
an account, then?

43:26.830 --> 43:27.789
Dou Zhao,

43:27.790 --> 43:28.930
I'll marry you.

43:30.900 --> 43:33.640
♪Fully aware of
the fleeting moments in the world♪

43:34.030 --> 43:36.399
♪Most love problems are hard to resolve♪

43:36.400 --> 43:40.780
♪For you, I rise again in this life♪

43:41.400 --> 43:44.390
♪Without regret♪

44:08.650 --> 44:10.940
♪I rise on tiptoes♪

44:11.390 --> 44:13.339
♪To kiss your brow♪

44:13.340 --> 44:18.760
♪From now on,
my heart needs no disguise♪

44:19.370 --> 44:21.590
♪Wrapped in frost and snow♪

44:22.050 --> 44:24.009
♪Standing side by side with you♪

44:24.010 --> 44:28.890
♪Witnessing
the magnificent world with you♪

44:29.230 --> 44:34.590
♪I hold onto this love
for the world to see♪

44:35.040 --> 44:39.310
♪Accumulated in this life,
now fulfilled♪

44:40.030 --> 44:45.580
♪Not heeding the people's advice♪

44:46.170 --> 44:52.520
♪Our love is as clear as the moon,
no false words in sight♪

44:53.320 --> 44:58.600
♪I close our distance without rest♪

44:58.650 --> 45:03.850
♪I devote my life and world
to your wishes♪

45:04.070 --> 45:07.010
♪Fully aware of
the fleeting moments in the world♪

45:07.420 --> 45:09.729
♪Most love problems are hard to resolve♪

45:09.730 --> 45:14.290
♪For you, I rise again in this life♪

45:14.630 --> 45:17.149
♪Without regret♪

45:17.150 --> 45:18.249
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

45:18.250 --> 45:19.169
(Every medical behaviour involved
and medicine used in the drama)

45:19.170 --> 45:20.370
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)
